{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":7465,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"慢走不送","timestamp":1592751059,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7474,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"笑死了，为啥说黑话，不就是因为正常的话都被封禁了吗🤣现在这也不让说了","timestamp":1592751111,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7489,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"关键是键盘政治家的平均素质。。。","timestamp":1592751205,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7548,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 这个角度感觉不完整，因为人的认识不是凭空来的。唯物的逻辑应该是首先因为不让人聊政治，接触不到一手史料，只能玩别人嚼烂的烂梗，然后反过来说键政圈大部分人水平不行。","timestamp":1592751481,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7950,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"却是人均政治素养不够，表达能力不够\n最要命的应该是不怎么学习，还有只讲立场和情绪吧","timestamp":1592753683,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7957,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 确实","timestamp":1592753692,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":8039,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果要求所有人在谈论政治时都具有完备的知识，那么就相当于所有人都不能说话，这样就正当化了统治阶级的所有所做所为，毕竟他们肯定比小老百姓懂政治，然而统治阶级不可能真的愿意也不可能有能力做到全心全意为人民服务。言论自由最大的意义是让底层的人能表达出自己的困境，倒逼统治者克服本身具有的惰性去解决问题，这才是键政的意义，而不是提出什么治国理念","timestamp":1592754104,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":8071,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 是啊，但是期待圣君是没有用的唉","timestamp":1592754220,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":8234,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赞成洞主。感觉整体的阴阳怪气和黑话流行的风气是对言论管制的直接结果。","timestamp":1592754994,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":8239,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 我们需要倡导学习政治知识，树立好的讨论政治的风气，提高讨论政治内容的质量","timestamp":1592755003,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":8306,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 滋瓷，但对于咱们这个小树洞来说，它和背后的开发团队承担不起这个责任。目前的形势下，没有给底层的人慢慢学习的时间和机会。一旦冲塔过火被封，大家流离失所不说，开发团队是要面临现实生活中的危险的。所以只能先保留火种从长计议","timestamp":1592755278,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":8382,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赞成洞主。直接封禁感觉还是不太行，希望树洞可以采取缓和一些的措施","timestamp":1592755691,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":20715,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 附议！封禁真的呵呵","timestamp":1592881424,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":20936,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":1484,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"自己学术不精啥也没读过没看过就怪封禁了？封禁尼玛了封禁","timestamp":1592882797,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":10,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":1484,"reply":14,"tag":"政治相关","text":"不让人聊政治，把人逼得只能讲黑话，再反过来说键政只会阴阳怪气，这赤裸裸的帝王史观可还行","timestamp":1592751034,"type":"text","updated_at":1618225918,"url":"","vote":{}}}